The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro
 Sunday, July 25, 2004  Good Morning Hello It's Sunday, July 25, 2004				 																Going, going, gone				 																																	Get your hands on cricket memorabilia at the Bless a Child Banquet  a charity auction attended by the spinner trio of Bishen Singh Bedi, E.A.S Prasanna and Chandrashekhar along with Navjyot Singh Sidhu and Mandira Bedi. At ITC Sonar Bangla, 7 pm. By invitation only. On canvas				 																																	Visit an exhibition of paintings organised by People for Animals Calcutta, at ITC Sonar Bangla, 11 am onwards. The artworks are results of a workshop by eminent artists. Worth the wait				 																																	Watch Showtimes Intezaar Andhere Tak, directed by Ardhendu Nayak, at Bhar-atiyam, Salt Lake, 6.30 pm. Film watch				 																																	Dont miss the screenings of Raja Sens Agyatobas, Atanu Ghoshs 700 sq feet and Robin Das Bis Koppur at Nandan II, noon, 3 pm and 6 pm respectively. 
